{"tid":786473,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【同足球撚有仇？】網傳戶外籃球架遭鎖上風扇罩　網民：好狠毒","createTime":"2018-08-20T03:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:38:03.000Z","uid":119778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bae49eb220cf4db9f4299913209bdda4a3ac615c","tid":786473,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/105636_b1ec89ff79fa430246b06e7a043f5a94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F105636_b1ec89ff79fa430246b06e7a043f5a94.png&h=d11954e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n室外籃球場是孕育不少灌籃高手的「搖籃」，有人更稱波友之間要「打過街場」先有共鳴。有網民昨晚（18日）於Facebook群組貼出相片，指有室外球場的籃球架被人以風扇外罩及鐵鎖鎖上，雖然未知涉事籃球架的地點及封架時間，但仍引起網民熱議。有人估計「封籃」是因為附近居民長期受球賽聲滋擾而「反擊」，有人則批評無論如何亦不應「阻人打波」，討論各種拆除風扇罩的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/105916_3009b254fdb77c7c1a76e771cd94aa66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F105916_3009b254fdb77c7c1a76e771cd94aa66.png&h=00768d84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/105920_a556fec2fe56e08ffb3ab6007412995a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F105920_a556fec2fe56e08ffb3ab6007412995a.png&h=348a5341&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/105922_ce89958be118c9142533cb8cee86a4d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F105922_ce89958be118c9142533cb8cee86a4d3.png&h=e9d84ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/105926_2d99cecefce5fac6a5b008d82978fbd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F105926_2d99cecefce5fac6a5b008d82978fbd4.png&h=ea48e267&s={SIZE